I"¡<h1 id="mailing-lists">Mailing lists</h1>

<p>These are the mailing lists that have been established for the Apache Logging Services project.</p>

<p>For questions regarding individual logging projects, please find use the mailing lists defined 
on the project site.</p>

<h3 id="generalloggingapacheorg">general@logging.apache.org</h3>

<p>General and public discussion related to the Logging project and itâ€™s children. Anyone may 
subscribe; only subscribers may post.</p>

